Author requires mention of original work in licence and contact informations for original project and author when this Softawre is being used for any use.

Some 3rd party librarires and tools may be used with separate or different licence.

Mainly:
FMOD Core API (vendor/fmod/LICENCE.TXT for more info).
gradrigo (vendor/gradrigo/LICENSE.txt)
ImGUI (vendor/ImGui/LICENSE.txt)
ImGuiFileDialog (vendor/ImGuiFileDialog/LICENSE)
libjpeg (vendor/libjpeg)
pugixml (vendor/pugixml/LICENSE.md)
GLFW (vendor/GLFW/LICENSE.md)
{fmt} (vendor/fmt/LICENSE.rst)
dirent (vendor/dirent/LICENSE)
DevIL (vendor/DevIL/LICENSE)
Assimp loader (vendor/Assimp/LICENSE)
